    "title": "cs_main lock not held when reindexing blocks on disk?",
    "body": "I've added an assertlockheld(cs_main) in coins.cpp, and I get the following stack trace when trying to reindex:\n\n```\nAssertion failed: lock cs_main not held in coins.cpp:194; locks held:\n```\n\n```\n#3  0x54beb616 in AssertLockHeldInternal (pszName=0x0, pszFile=0x1 <error: Cannot access memory at address 0x1>, nLine=nLine@entry=194, cs=0x54e08b48 <cs_main>) at sync.cpp:149\n#4  0x54bb52ec in CCoinsViewCache::Flush (this=0x54e7b9f8) at coins.cpp:194\n#5  0x54afee4c in FlushStateToDisk (state=..., mode=mode@entry=FLUSH_STATE_PERIODIC) at main.cpp:1805\n#6  0x54b069d2 in ActivateBestChain (state=..., pblock=pblock@entry=0x2f9fed08) at main.cpp:2127\n#7  0x54b06ef2 in ProcessNewBlock (state=..., pfrom=pfrom@entry=0x0, pblock=pblock@entry=0x2f9fed08, dbp=dbp@entry=0x2f9feddc) at main.cpp:2579\n#8  0x54b0739e in LoadExternalBlockFile (fileIn=fileIn@entry=0x2fa007a8, dbp=dbp@entry=0x2f9feddc) at main.cpp:3191\n#9  0x54ad574c in ThreadImport (vImportFiles=std::vector of length 0, capacity 0) at init.cpp:417\n```\n",
